Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟我一起來嗎？千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會做奇怪的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不危險吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是釣竿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說那個，這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的釣場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地裡只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要搭往東京的班機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能在這裡\N再待40多分鐘而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我當初的作戰目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就是想帶妳來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻因為各種事而繞了一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，釣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定30分鐘就可以釣到大魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就很難說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟妳在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得什麼都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是釣上超乎想像的大魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是從恐怖的危險中逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的這麼覺得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有妳在，我現在才能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就來試試\N你所說的這種好運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯛魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是鯨魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不能否定這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要把牠釣回家去喔，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
